## Your Coaching/Consulting Launch Plan

**Step 1: Define Your Offer (Week 1)**
- Pick your level (group, 1-on-1, consulting, advisory)
- Define your ideal client specifically
- Define the transformation you provide
- Write your offer in 3 sentences

**Step 2: Set Your Pricing (Week 1)**
- Research 3 competitors
- Pick price 10-30% higher or lower
- Set your initial price
- Plan to raise it in 90 days

**Step 3: Create Your Sales Page (Week 2)**
- Write copy that speaks to their pain
- Show your framework/process
- Share your results (case study or before/after)
- List clear next steps (apply, call, etc.)

**Step 4: Generate Leads (Week 2-3)**
- List 10 ideal clients (who you want to work with)
- Email them directly or call them
- Offer free 30-min strategy call
- Schedule 5 calls

**Step 5: Close Your First Client (Week 3-4)**
- Run your sales calls
- Ask if they want to move forward
- Send offer details via email
- Close 1 paying client

**By day 30:** You have 1 paying coaching/consulting client generating $5K-$25K revenue

---

## Scaling: From 1 to 5 Clients

Once you have 1 client:

**Months 1-3:** Land 1-2 more (3 total)

**Months 3-6:** Keep at 3 maximum (1-on-1 coaching is time-intensive)

**Alternative:** Launch group program (20 people) instead of individual clients

**Goal by Month 6:** Either 3 high-ticket clients ($50K+ annual) OR 1 group program ($15K-$30K annual)

You're now at $50K-$80K annual revenue from coaching/consulting. Time to build digital products to scale further.
